                  "revisionId": 2588304,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Stunning Speed is additive with similar mods. For example, a Sicarus with a max rank Stunning Speed and Sure Shot will have a 6% × (1 + 30% + 90%) = 13.2% status chance."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Stunning Speed",
                  "pageId": 110784,
                  "revisionId": 2588304,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This mod doesn't directly reduce reload times; it increases reload speed. The calculations are far different, and that can cause some confusion."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Stunning Speed",
                  "pageId": 110784,
                  "revisionId": 2588304,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The calculation of reload time using reload speed as a variable is almost the same with melee charge speed, which is Base Reload Time÷(1+ Reload Speed Bonus) ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Stunning Speed",
                  "pageId": 110784,
                  "revisionId": 2588304,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The 40% reload speed bonus at max rank equates to a ~29% reduction to reload times. You can calculate the reduction as 1-(1÷(1+s)), where s is your total reload speed bonus."
                }
              },
              {
